  "texts": [
    "Since the probabilistic view (Fig. 2) gave consistent results across tasks and model sizes, we focus on one task (translation) and one model size (70B, i.e., d = 8192).",
    "Embedding spheres.",
    "Output token embeddings (rows of the unembedding matrix U) and latents h cohabitate the same d-dimensional Euclidean space.",
    "In fact, due to RMS-normalization (Sec.",
    "3.1), latents by construction live on a hypersphere of radius √ d ≈ 90.1."
  ]
